This project was generated with the **FARM Stack Framework** using the `ecommerce` template. It provides a FastAPI backend with product, cart and order APIs and a React frontend with shopping cart and checkout flows.

## Development

Install dependencies and start the development servers:

```bash
# Frontend
cd apps/web && npm install && npm run dev
# Backend
cd ../api && pip install -r requirements.txt && uvicorn src.main:app --reload
```

